    33	 * @param {import('@tevm/utils').Hex} salt - A 32-byte value as a hex string that makes the address unique
    34	 * @param {import('@tevm/utils').Hex} code - The contract creation bytecode (not the deployed bytecode)
    35	 * @returns {Address} The deterministic contract address that will be generated
    36	 * @throws {Create2ContractAddressError} If salt is not 32 bytes or if other inputs are invalid
    37	 *
    38	 * @example
    39	 * ```javascript
